en_100495_0	A fuel bowser siphoning oil at a filling station in Nelumdeniya exploded and caught fire this afternoon.
en_100495_1	Police Media Spokesman SSP Ajith Rohana said that no casualties were reported after the explosion.
en_100495_2	However, fire fighters were summoned from Kandy to douse the blaze.
en_100495_3	Meanwhile Police request the public to use alternative roads as Colombo Kandy road has been temporarily closed at Nelum-deniya. pix by - madawalanews
